OL,3,CState pension deadline: What is it and
OL,4,Cwho should top up National Insurance?
OL,6,FWords by Tommaso Dimiddio, ITV News
OL,7,FProducer
OL,9,FPeople in Britain aged between 40 and
OL,10,F73 have until April to potentially
OL,11,Fboost their state pension by thousands
OL,12,Fof pounds.
OL,14,FThey can do so by checking their
OL,15,FNational Insurance (NI) records and
OL,16,Ffilling in any gaps going back as far
OL,17,Fas April 2006.
