OL,6,FThis will increase their chances of
OL,7,Fbanking enough years of NI payments to
OL,8,Fqualify for a full state pension when
OL,9,Fthey retire.
OL,11,FWhy does the number of National
OL,12,FInsurance years matter?
OL,14,FConsumer expert Martin Lewis says
OL,15,FNational Insurance is a bit like a
OL,16,Ftoken you can earn for each tax year.
