OL,3,CState pension deadline: What is it and
OL,4,Cwho should top up National Insurance?
OL,6,FThe more tokens you get, the bigger
OL,7,Fthe proportion of the weekly state
OL,8,Fpension you receive once you hit
OL,9,Fretirement age. The state pension
OL,10,Fcurrently stands at #221.20 per week.
OL,12,FTo qualify for a "token" in any given
OL,13,Ftax year, you have to have sufficient
OL,14,FNational Insurance credit for that
OL,15,Fyear.
OL,17,FYou need at least 10 qualifying NI
OL,18,Fyears to get some state pension.
OL,20,FTo get the full state pension, you
OL,21,Fneed around 35 qualifying NI years.
