OL,3,CState pension deadline: What is it and
OL,4,Cwho should top up National Insurance?
OL,6,FThe deadline of April 5 has been set
OL,7,Ffor people to check their national
OL,8,Finsurance (NI) records and fill in any
OL,9,Fgaps going back as far as April 2006.
OL,11,FFrom April 6, people will generally
OL,12,Fonly be able to make voluntary NI
OL,13,Fcontributions for the previous six tax
OL,14,Fyears, in line with normal time limits.
OL,16,FHowever, the Government has said that
OL,17,Fthose who cannot get through ahead of
OL,18,Fthe deadline can use an online call
OL,19,Fback request form.
